---
title: Black Bean Chipotle Enchiladas with Smashed Avocado, Sticky Wedges and Charred Corn Slaw
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Black Bean Chipotle Enchiladas are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R37_W04_UK_SSFV19063-4__MAIN_low-68acb69b.jpg
